This directory contains: 
	- Common CMake files used by all platforms
	- Common CMake utilities and extensions that are useful


NOTE: Add FindCUDA.cmake and FindGLEW.cmake etc.


external
=========
the subdirs in "external" are all git submodules. That is, they are outside git repos imported into our own repo. To update submodules to their remote head we run: 

git submodule update


